#### Description
* Some hypotheses are hard to test in practice
* However often you can tap experience or experise
* You need to identify the expert and determine their credibility

#### Tips
* Make sure the expert indeed has the requisite knowledge or experience
* Sometimes a single expert is enough, sometimes you might want a second one
* Sometimes your hypothesis is proven by analogy or observation (hypothesis: a small robotic   vacccum cleaner can be built for under $1000)
